{"tid":1522901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有警員用曱甴形容示威者","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:59:11.000Z","uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f46e757a50b80eef1f9dd627d73983d3891d466","tid":1522901,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"男子朗讀「不徇私，不畏懼，不對他人懷惡意」<br />\n即遭防暴警察包圍<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(22:10) 防暴警察於中央圖書館及天后清場後，折返銅鑼灣渣甸街，到達燈籠洲街市後。有一名年輕男子對警察朗讀「不徇私，不畏懼，不對他人懷惡意」。他隨即遭十多名防暴警察包圍，要求查核其身份證和身上所有物品。該名男子隨即舉起雙手，但警員仍對他指罵。<br />\n<br />\n擾攘15分鐘後，警員才放行，有警員稱「依加係你懷惡意，明唔明？差人做嘢唔X洗你教。」<br />\n<br />\n獨媒記者拍攝期間，有傳媒聯絡警員稱「唔好咁多事啦，曱甴就由X得佢啦。」記者繼續採訪，再有其他警員稱「影嚟都嘥氣，成日用個cam對住我哋。」<br />\n<br />\n【不斷更新】人大831五周年 民陣遊行被禁<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UocEdZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UocEdZ&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=41088161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UocEdZ</a><br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=faa5dddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=44cdc58e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"},{"pid":"e571bbbca07f8dc457e8df2688482fbfd2f578b3","tid":1522901,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"Hai"},{"pid":"cdc941f6513852cadb3708efe3b964482a1efb04","tid":1522901,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset